text: California farmworkers provide more than 1/3 of the country’s vegetables & 2/3 of its fruits. Workers are considered "essential" but many are undocumented, lack health insurance & don’t qualify for federal COVID-19 relief. Here are the challenges they face https://t.co/0Ov4gRZLys
